{"tid":2463331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌你老母 民主黨 快撚d全體死全家","createTime":"2021-03-26T15:13:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T15:27:27.000Z","uid":25825,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2a9dcc774b4893b97f779a7740ea34e994da6362","tid":2463331,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:13:29.000Z","msg":"【政情】民主黨增設內地小組「乳鴿」有微言　張文光任顧問助了解國情<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=428962&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D428962%26refer%3DShare&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWmsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=a22dd51e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D428962%26refer%3DShare&h=386bd921\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=428962&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">民主黨多名年青中委，包括副主席梁翊婷表明有意加入，但在北京打壓民主派之時，籌組「內地及政制事務委員會」，</span>黨內個別「乳鴿」有微言，不滿事前既不知情，又指黨核心解說委員會時，提到要認清形勢及減少錯誤，覺得「認錯意味」太濃。據悉，民主黨在復活節期間，特別舉行交流會，預料屆時將是討論焦點。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">我屌你老母 乜撚嘢<br />\n內地及政制事務委員會<br />\n<br />\n<strong>副主席梁翊婷 你屙尿既時候舉起左腳定右腳？</strong><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民主黨一直主張和理非路線，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">但有「老鴿」坦言，反修例一役，激進聲放大，民主派多名骨幹被指已踩紅線，有必要協助年青黨員認清國情，</span></span>尤其國安法實施後，從政風險甚高，抗爭路線隨時撼頭埋牆，認為從政必須務實，認清北京的治港方針，知己知彼避免踩地雷。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">支那民主黨幾時發聲明<br />\n#支持新彊棉花<br />\n#支持種族滅絕？</span></span>"},{"pid":"cd74ea90f0a174e2604a065a3c83b25ed72838dd","tid":2463331,"uid":25825,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:14:29.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">香港民主黨<br />\n#支持新彊棉花<br />\n#支持種族滅絕</span></span>"},{"pid":"00c76725239039743936b00cc2e6d1cba5e2ad5a","tid":2463331,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:15:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8139d014e50b5b565e90b0e1422d7c14107283b4","tid":2463331,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8d8870ed11b336a98ef692c9a82a384fd2e50d","tid":2463331,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:16:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"782c68fef94fa67b6b80bb7291375658073aa9ff","tid":2463331,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"041482325ce22a256b101df3e0272d672a0be6f3","tid":2463331,"uid":306614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cd74ea90f0a174e2604a065a3c83b25ed72838dd","tid":2463331,"uid":25825,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:14:29.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">香港民主黨<br />\n#支持新彊棉花<br />\n#支持種族滅絕</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:16:42.000Z","msg":"係囉 CLS"},{"pid":"c20541b2697e0fae94e0e5ead2a31e5d0180b82c","tid":2463331,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8139d014e50b5b565e90b0e1422d7c14107283b4","tid":2463331,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:16:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e06df2a7c9ef49d78eab6a849a0159cd06aa6b53","tid":2463331,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c8172b3ed745e8342da9888b74528f130a1b05","tid":2463331,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi